  <name>Cred Manager</name>
  <summary>Secure API Key Management</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Cred Manager is a secure, local-only desktop application for managing API keys,
      credentials, and sensitive data with enterprise-grade security.
    </p>
    <p>
      Features include Argon2 password hashing, SQLCipher database encryption,
      biometric authentication support, and project-based organization.
    </p>
    <p>
      All data is stored locally with strong encryption - no network connectivity required.
    </p>
